的。这位音乐家在演出前的小插曲中谈到这首歌曲时说道：“我是 Metallica 获准在<em>AGT</em>上演奏的第一人。我真的想让 Metallica 感到自豪。”</p><p> 《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-guitar-prodigy-maya-neelakantan-join-testament-on-stage-3797516">Watch》吉他神童 Maya Neelakantan 加入《Testament》舞台后</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
新音乐纪录片讲述苏格兰无名女子乐队的故事https://www.nme.com/news/film/new-music-doc-to-tell-story-of-scotlands-unsung-girl-bands-3797509?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=new-music-doc-讲述苏格兰无名女子乐队的故事Max PilleyThu, 26 Sep 2024 20:37:19 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsIndiePophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3797509 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这部电影将记录几十年来美国最伟大的无名女子组合，包括 The McKinleys、Strawberry Switchblade 和 Sophisticated Boom Boom</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/new-music-doc-to-tell-story-of-scotlands-unsung-girl-bands-3797509">讲述苏格兰无名女子乐队故事的新音乐纪录片</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_DirectorsHeadshot_CarlaJEastonBlairYoung_CreditEuanRobertson-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一部新的纪录片《<i>从昨天开始：苏格兰女子乐队不为人知的故事</i>》将揭示苏格兰过去 50 年来最伟大的无名女子组合。</p><p>这部长篇电影将于 10 月 18 日起在英国影院上映，届时英国许多最具开拓性、另类的女性流行音乐和独立艺术家将发表自己的声音，记录她们在男性主导的行业中的反抗和突破创新。几十年来。放映门票可<a href="http://sinceyesterdayfilm.com/lander" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>找到。</p><p>这部电影由音乐家、格拉斯哥和谐乐队 TeenCanteen 前成员卡拉·J·伊斯顿 (Carla J. Easton) 编剧和导演，联合导演布莱尔·杨 (Blair Young) 曾为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/belle-and-sebastian">Belle &amp; Sebastian</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/teenage-fanclub">Teenage Fanclub</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/biffy-clyro">Biffy Clyro</a>制作过视频。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="2024 年 DOC&#39;N ROLL |从昨天开始苏格兰女子乐队不为人知的故事 - 预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VOYYmM7e0sw?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <i>《Yesterday》</i>将讲述麦金利乐队 (The McKinleys) 的崛起，这是第一支苏格兰女子乐队，于 1964 年凭借单曲《甜蜜而温柔的浪漫》(Sweet and Tender Romance) 获得排行榜上的成功，并将吸收诸如草莓弹簧刀 (Strawberry Switchblade) 等团体的影响力（影片的片名正是由其标志性歌曲命名） 、 精致的 Boom Boom、The Ettes、The Hedrons、他最新的 Flame、Hello Skinny、Lung Leg 和 Sunset Gun。</p><p>该片于上个月在爱丁堡国际电影节闭幕式上进行了全球首映，并将于 10 月 18 日在格拉斯哥的首映之夜进行特别放映，并在 Mono 举办一晚的映后演出，并由 Sophisticated Boom Boom 重制一晚只为特殊的表演。麦金利乐队 (McKinleys) 的珍妮特·加拉格尔 (Jeanette Gallagher)、歌曲创作团体 Hen Hoose 和 This Mortal Coil 的路易斯·鲁特科斯基 (Louise Rutkowski) 也将在活动中表演。 </p><figure id="attachment_3797510" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3797510" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3797510" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_Poster_Landscape_LowRes-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_Poster_Landscape_LowRes-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_Poster_Landscape_LowRes-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_Poster_Landscape_LowRes-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_Poster_Landscape_LowRes-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_Poster_Landscape_LowRes-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/SinceYesterday_Poster_Landscape_LowRes-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3797510" class="wp-caption-text"> 《从昨天开始》海报。图片来源：宇宙猫</figcaption></figure><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="麦金利夫妇 - “甜蜜而温柔的浪漫” 1964" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/8MzmzqZJQjQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="草莓弹簧刀——从昨天开始" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/x7QPBzAJ_io?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>伊斯顿谈到这个项目时说道：“自从我第一次向布莱尔提出制作一部关于 2016 年在苏格兰组建乐队的女性历史的纪录片的想法以来，我们一直很高兴能让观众听到我们所有的伟大音乐。已经知道了，然后是我们随后发现的所有音乐。但更重要的是，它让人们听到那些创作音乐的女性讲述她们的故事的经历，这是她们以前从未真正有机会做的事情。”</p><p>杨补充道：“我很高兴人们能够在电影中以及通过与放映和其他活动一起发生的现场活动来听到这种音乐并认识这些令人惊叹的角色，我希望它能在某种程度上帮助改变一些事情。”未来的乐队。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/new-music-doc-to-tell-story-of-scotlands-unsung-girl-bands-3797509">讲述苏格兰无名女子乐队故事的新音乐纪录片</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
